text: Heliophanus charlesi is a jumping spider species in the genus Heliophanus. It was first described by Wanda Wesołowska in 2003 and lives in South Africa. ==References== Category:Salticidae Category:Spiders of South Africa Category:Spiders described in 2003 Category:Taxa named by Wanda Wesołowska
title: Heliophanus charlesi
